msgid ""
"Django relies on user input in some cases (e.g. "
":func:`django.contrib.auth.views.login` and :doc:`i18n "
"</topics/i18n/index>`) to redirect the user to an \"on success\" URL. The "
"security checks for these redirects (namely "
