#: ../../../../sources/1.9/docs/releases/1.7.txt:777
msgid ""
"It is now possible to use ``None`` as a query value for the :lookup:`iexact`"
" lookup."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../sources/1.9/docs/releases/1.7.txt:780
msgid ""
