#: ../../../../sources/1.9/docs/releases/1.8.txt:308
msgid ""
"The SMTP :class:`~django.core.mail.backends.smtp.EmailBackend` now supports "
"setting the ``timeout`` parameter with the :setting:`EMAIL_TIMEOUT` setting."
