#: ../../../../sources/1.9/docs/releases/1.9.txt:423
msgid ""
"The :djadmin:`dumpdata` command output is now deterministically ordered. "
"Moreover, when the ``--output`` option is specified, it also shows a "
"progress bar in the terminal."
