#: ../../../../sources/1.9/docs/releases/1.9.txt:430
msgid ""
"The :djadmin:`startapp` command creates an ``apps.py`` file. Since it "
"doesn't use ``default_app_config`` (:ref:`a discouraged API <configuring-"
